      <title>中国小型股崩盘表明，如果没有市场救援，将会发生什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-s-small-cap-crash-shows-what-happens-without-market-rescue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果北京方面未能落实备受期待的救援行动，中国规模最小的股票将发出警告，称世界第二大股市可能面临下行风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-s-small-cap-crash-shows-what-happens-without-market-rescue</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国承诺市场稳定，沪深300指数迎来五年期低的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-pledges-market-stability-csi-300-hits-5-yr-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继上周的暴跌之后，中国投资者正在评估政策制定者为稳定低迷市场而做出的最新承诺。由于中国股市跌至 5 年低点，周一小盘股普遍下跌 8%。丽贝卡·钟·威尔金斯报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-pledges-market-stability-csi-300-hits-5-yr-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及英镑在黑市上上涨，缓解了贬值的道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/egypt-s-pound-gains-on-black-market-easing-path-for-devaluation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及英镑在当地美元黑市上大幅走强，此举可能有助于为这个现金短缺的国家下一次广泛预期的货币贬值奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/egypt-s-pound-gains-on-black-market-easing-path-for-devaluation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经合组织告诉各国央行，现在欢呼通胀胜利还为时过早</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/oecd-forecasts-central-banks-still-face-inflation-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经合组织表示，世界主要央行在对抗通胀方面绝不能放松警惕，因为现在判断大幅加息是否遏制了潜在的价格压力还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/oecd-forecasts-central-banks-still-face-inflation-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>空中客车公司正在与沙特阿拉伯就空中加油机订单进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/airbus-in-talks-with-saudi-arabia-for-military-air-tanker-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[空中客车公司表示，由于沙特阿拉伯希望增强其空军能力，该公司正在就向沙特阿拉伯出售更多 A330 加油机进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/airbus-in-talks-with-saudi-arabia-for-military-air-tanker-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:57:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔发表言论后欧洲股市暂停；联合信贷银行跳跃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/european-stocks-edge-up-after-powell-comments-unicredit-jumps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市变化不大，主要股的涨幅被汽车制造商的跌幅所抵消。投资者仔细考虑了好坏参半的财报以及美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔周末的言论，后者重申市场可能需要等到 3 月份之后才会降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/european-stocks-edge-up-after-powell-comments-unicredit-jumps</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:19:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能矿工表示在赞比亚发现了巨大的铜矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/bill-gates-backed-miner-finds-world-class-zambian-copper-deposit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KoBold Metals 是一家利用人工智能探索绿色能源转型关键材料的矿业初创公司，该公司表示在赞比亚发现了巨大的铜矿床。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/bill-gates-backed-miner-finds-world-class-zambian-copper-deposit</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 07:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行破坏了私人信贷创纪录的阿多纳交易 20 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/banks-spoil-private-credit-s-record-ardonagh-deal-with-2-billion-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以摩根士丹利和高盛集团为首的一批华尔街贷款机构突然介入，为 Ardonagh Group Ltd. 管理约 20 亿美元的债券销售，这是银行相对于私人信贷公司的一次关键胜利，后者曾向 Ardonagh Group Ltd. 提供了创纪录的贷款。英国保险经纪人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/banks-spoil-private-credit-s-record-ardonagh-deal-with-2-billion-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 02:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美联储利率前景削弱地缘政治溢价，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔平息了三月份利率将下降的预期，油价扭转了早些时候的上涨趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:26:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔的国债进一步下滑；股票涨跌互现：市场休整</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔降低了降息的希望，美国国债延续抛售，美元上涨。]]></description>
